
* From 1942 to 1989 the closing game of the season was the Champion of Champions game. It was held between the League Champion and the Cup Champion. When the same teams wins both championships, it is declared "Campeonisimo". From the season 2002-03 to 2005-06, it was held between the Apertura Champion and the Clausura Champion.


